text.text: Visited in Dec 2022, stayed in Haritha hotel - it had no restaurant then. This hotel was life saver - ate there 3 times every day. No fancy food, but reasonably clean, prompt service, friendly owner, decent tiffin & meals. Curd rice & Chicken Fry dinner was good. About 2 km before Haritha. Five star considering it is in Alampur.
